ZH: 我们和孩子们睡在篷车的床上，观赏星空。
EN: We laid on the camper van bed with our children, stargazing.

ZH: 这辆篷车的内部空间布局非常合理。
EN: The interior layout of this motorhome is very well-designed.

ZH: 我们在山间找到一个小空地，停下篷车搭帐篷。
EN: We found a small clearing in the mountains, parked the campervan, and set up tents.
